Personal Story Posts

Now, many of these content types can be mixed and matched. You
can write a post that talks about a problem and then share your
experience on how to solve it. I say that because the next
concept is using your personal experiences and stories to better
connect with your audience. On the one hand, you can use this to
try to connect better. I believe =E2=80=8BAlex Freberg=E2=80=8B (
